==English==

===Noun===
'''[[benefactive]] [[case]]'''

#{{grammar}}: [[case]] used to indicate [[beneficiary]], or the receiver of the benefit. It corresponds roughly to the English prepositions '''for''', '''for the benefit of''', and '''intended for'''. [[Basque]] and [[Quechua]] are languages with a benefactive case.

